sequenceDiagram
    participant Local as 本地 verify.py
    participant Remote as AIYJY-litellm
    participant Proxy as LiteLLM Dev Proxy
    participant DB as Postgres SpendLogs
    participant Report as 本地报告

    Local->>Remote: 上传远程验证脚本
    Remote->>Proxy: /key/generate 临时测试 key
    Remote->>Proxy: /v1/models
    Proxy-->>Remote: 只返回 9 个产品模型
    loop 内部模型直连
        Remote->>Proxy: 请求 hidden/internal model
        Proxy-->>Remote: 403 或 model not found
    end
    loop 每个产品模型
        Remote->>Proxy: 正常 /v1/responses
        Proxy->>DB: 写 SpendLogs
        Remote->>DB: 查询 model_group/model_id/api_base/status
    end
    loop 每个 fallback case
        Remote->>Proxy: mock_testing_fallbacks=true
        Proxy->>DB: 写主失败与 fallback 结果
        Remote->>DB: 轮询 case_id 或时间窗证据
    end
    Remote->>Proxy: finally /key/delete
    Remote-->>Local: JSON 验证结果
    Local->>Report: 写 Markdown + JSON
